  "texts": [
    "In the second step, each coarse-grained type entity was classified into finer-grained entity classes using a classification algorithm combining dictionary and maximum entropy model.",
    "The dictionary-based recognizers used lists of words built on expert-annotated data 35.",
    "For data that cannot be matched, the word embedding vectors, context vectors, word cluster clustering information and coarse-grained entity category information for each entity were passed through a simple mapping function.",
    "The final mapping results were used as entity features for classification probability prediction through a maximum entropy model.",
    "A typical synthesis procedure in the electrocatalytic reduction literature contains information on the prepared and target materials, synthesis operations and operating conditions."
